00:01:45.360 --> 00:01:47.590
Corinthians 13, meditating on that,

00:01:47.600 --> 00:01:50.149
and getting that word of what the Bible

00:01:50.159 --> 00:01:52.230
says about love taking no account of a

00:01:52.240 --> 00:01:53.149
suffered

00:01:53.159 --> 00:01:55.830
wrong when people do you wrong and all

00:01:55.840 --> 00:01:57.670
