00:01:57.680 --> 00:01:59.670
that He's going to do it. Having an

00:01:59.680 --> 00:02:02.230
expectation for manifestations,

00:02:02.240 --> 00:02:04.709
because expectation brings

00:02:04.719 --> 00:02:08.389
