00:02:18.959 --> 00:02:22.790
today. I do not want to go away and have

00:02:22.800 --> 00:02:25.589
another lukewarm service that

00:02:25.599 --> 00:02:27.949
everybody kind of feels was okay,

00:02:27.959 --> 00:02:31.270
whatever, bypassing another week. I

00:02:31.280 --> 00:02:35.670
know from glory to glory He's changing

00:02:35.680 --> 00:02:39.430
me. I want that so bad. The only thing

00:02:39.440 --> 00:02:41.110
