00:02:53.040 --> 00:02:54.949
"Faith cometh by hearing, hearing by the word

00:02:54.959 --> 00:02:57.190
of God,"you know. And R.W.

00:02:57.190 --> 00:02:57.200
Schambach,

00:02:57.200 --> 00:02:58.589
all the

00:02:58.589 --> 00:02:58.599
greats.

00:02:58.599 --> 00:03:01.110
I said, "My goodness, Lord, help

00:03:01.120 --> 00:03:03.430
me. If I'm a closer, I don't want to let

00:03:03.440 --> 00:03:05.509
these guys down. I don't want to let you

00:03:05.519 --> 00:03:08.470
down. I want to finish strong. Lord, let

00:03:08.480 --> 00:03:10.229
us do something big for you

00:03:10.239 --> 00:03:12.350
because the word is working mightily in

00:03:12.360 --> 00:03:15.589
me. The word is working mightily in me.

00:03:15.599 --> 00:03:17.830
Do you believe it? Do you believe

00:03:17.830 --> 00:03:17.840
