00:03:48.869 --> 00:03:48.879
He

00:03:48.879 --> 00:03:52.550
said, love from 1 Corinthians

00:03:52.560 --> 00:03:55.350
13. Get in that love. Okay, so if I'm

00:03:55.360 --> 00:03:57.509
walking in love, and you

00:03:57.519 --> 00:03:59.509
are love, and you're inside of me, and I'm

00:03:59.519 --> 00:04:01.509
