00:05:16.800 --> 00:05:17.749
you're talking about the Holy

00:05:17.759 --> 00:05:19.749
Ghost. You're talking about the end times,

00:05:19.759 --> 00:05:22.469
"Jesus is coming. The end times are

00:05:22.469 --> 00:05:22.479
