00:10:55.710 --> 00:10:55.720
me.'But

00:10:55.720 --> 00:10:57.910
after you get all these little

00:10:57.920 --> 00:10:59.509
pricks and things, and Braden

00:10:59.519 --> 00:11:01.110
finally, it was the grace of God

00:11:01.120 --> 00:11:02.389
watching a YouTube video that we were

00:11:02.399 --> 00:11:03.590
able to—because he said, 'Daddy, we're

00:11:03.600 --> 00:11:04.630
going to have to buy a new computer.

00:11:04.640 --> 00:11:05.990
This computer's

00:11:05.990 --> 00:11:06.000
gone.'And

00:11:06.000 --> 00:11:08.949
watching a YouTube video,

00:11:08.959 --> 00:11:11.590
he fixed it. Thank God. Took him all

00:11:11.600 --> 00:11:14.150
day long Thursday. All day long, we

00:11:14.160 --> 00:11:16.150
didn't have it. And

00:11:16.160 --> 00:11:18.550
I told him, I said, 'Whatever happens

00:11:18.560 --> 00:11:21.949
happens, buddy. We'll make it

00:11:21.949 --> 00:11:21.959
work.'Whenever

00:11:21.959 --> 00:11:24.710
the enemy

00:11:24.720 --> 00:11:27.110
comes in and he tries to test

00:11:27.120 --> 00:11:29.829
you to see if he's getting to you by

00:11:29.839 --> 00:11:33.389
how you react. How are you reacting

00:11:33.399 --> 00:11:36.710
to the septic tank getting run over, the

00:11:36.720 --> 00:11:38.630
water line, and the water

00:11:38.640 --> 00:11:40.550
flooding my bathroom and ruining

00:11:40.550 --> 00:11:40.560
it,

00:11:40.560 --> 00:11:43.110
and I had to go and fix all that, the

00:11:43.120 --> 00:11:46.310
boards falling down from the storm?

00:11:46.320 --> 00:11:49.630
All these little things.

00:11:49.640 --> 00:11:52.630
The enemy tried to

00:11:52.640 --> 00:11:55.550
get you all in your thoughts,

00:11:55.560 --> 00:11:58.630
but it all goes back to 1

00:11:58.640 --> 00:12:00.670
Corinthians

00:12:00.680 --> 00:12:04.069
13. Will you walk in love? Will you

00:12:04.079 --> 00:12:07.829
allow your fruit to shine to men? And

00:12:07.839 --> 00:12:09.470
whenever the devil's trying to get your

00:12:09.480 --> 00:12:12.069
joy with all these little things and it

00:12:12.079 --> 00:12:13.550
all adds up, like I

00:12:13.560 --> 00:12:16.389
said, thousands, and my flesh, like I

00:12:16.399 --> 00:12:18.750
said, I

00:12:18.750 --> 00:12:18.760
was—wow.

00:12:18.760 --> 00:12:22.710
Okay. So, whenever all that's

00:12:22.720 --> 00:12:24.150
coming on you and all that's going on

00:12:24.160 --> 00:12:25.990
and you have the opportunity to walk in

00:12:26.000 --> 00:12:29.550
love, right? Walk in

00:12:29.560 --> 00:12:32.829
love. The Bible says, 'Take no thought,

00:12:32.829 --> 00:12:32.839
saying.'Take

00:12:32.839 --> 00:12:36.790
no thought, saying. Why?

00:12:36.800 --> 00:12:38.230
Because out of the abundance of the

00:12:38.240 --> 00:12:40.150
heart, the mouth speaks. And the

00:12:40.160 --> 00:12:43.190
devil cannot read your thoughts. The

00:12:43.200 --> 00:12:45.509
devil can't go around looking, 'Am I

00:12:45.519 --> 00:12:47.910
getting to him?'So the only way he can

00:12:47.920 --> 00:12:49.990
know if he's getting

00:12:50.000 --> 00:12:52.310
to you is by how you're responding on

00:12:52.320 --> 00:12:53.910
the outside in the natural. Because the

00:12:53.920 --> 00:12:55.310
devil's a flesh

00:12:55.320 --> 00:12:57.350
devil. He doesn't get anything by the

00:12:57.360 --> 00:12:59.110
spirit of God. He has to move by the

00:12:59.120 --> 00:13:03.269
flesh. And he's not

00:13:03.269 --> 00:13:03.279
omnipresent.

00:13:03.279 --> 00:13:06.150
He is either with you or

00:13:06.160 --> 00:13:07.750
whatever. He's not like

00:13:07.760 --> 00:13:10.870
the Holy Spirit, right? So,

00:13:10.880 --> 00:13:12.790
his demons are looking to go back and

00:13:12.800 --> 00:13:14.790
report to him, 'This worked and this

00:13:14.800 --> 00:13:16.790
didn't work.'But when you show the love

00:13:16.800 --> 00:13:18.310
of God, you pass the test. That's what

00:13:18.320 --> 00:13:20.550
I'm trying to tell y'all. When you get

00:13:20.560 --> 00:13:22.310
cut off on the road, when you do these

00:13:22.320 --> 00:13:23.750
things and people treat you badly at the

00:13:23.750 --> 00:13:23.760
restaurant—you

00:13:23.760 --> 00:13:25.430
might have a bad server

00:13:25.440 --> 00:13:26.949
at the restaurant. She might give you

00:13:26.959 --> 00:13:29.030
bad service and you show love and say,

00:13:29.030 --> 00:13:29.040
'I'll

00:13:29.040 --> 00:13:32.230
give her a good tip anyway.

00:13:32.240 --> 00:13:33.870
She doesn't deserve it.'And

00:13:33.870 --> 00:13:33.880
you might

00:13:33.880 --> 00:13:36.870
want to just tell

00:13:36.880 --> 00:13:39.509
her boss, 'She's the most lousy server

00:13:39.519 --> 00:13:41.790
I've ever had. She didn't get my drinks

00:13:41.800 --> 00:13:44.069
refilled. She didn't give me good

00:13:44.079 --> 00:13:46.629
service the whole time. I'm telling

00:13:46.639 --> 00:13:48.550
you what, I want to let this girl have a

00:13:48.560 --> 00:13:51.430
piece of my mind,'you know, but you go

00:13:51.440 --> 00:13:54.550
and you say, 'Honey, I know this may not

00:13:54.560 --> 00:13:56.629
be your calling, but I'm going to bless

00:13:56.639 --> 00:13:58.350
you anyway and show you

00:13:58.350 --> 00:13:58.360
love,'you

00:13:58.360 --> 00:14:01.750
know, 20 bucks or whatever. I

00:14:01.760 --> 00:14:03.910
don't know, that's a big tip, I'm just

00:14:03.920 --> 00:14:05.829
saying you give them a big

00:14:05.839 --> 00:14:08.509
tip. They may say, 'Hey, I

00:14:08.519 --> 00:14:11.030
can't

00:14:11.040 --> 00:14:12.470
believe how I treated you'or whatever.

00:14:12.480 --> 00:14:15.269
I don't know, I just try

00:14:15.279 --> 00:14:17.509
to show God's love until the point of

00:14:17.519 --> 00:14:18.990
where it's

00:14:19.000 --> 00:14:21.670
painful to my flesh because there's

00:14:21.680 --> 00:14:23.430
something more about it in the glory, is

00:14:23.440 --> 00:14:25.230
what I'm trying to tell you

00:14:25.240 --> 00:14:28.470
all. Where is the glory? Where's the

00:14:28.480 --> 00:14:30.150
outpouring of the spirit of God? Like

00:14:30.160 --> 00:14:32.310
we've never seen it before. The Lord

00:14:32.320 --> 00:14:34.790
told me, he said, 'Brandon, Jesus did

00:14:34.800 --> 00:14:37.030
not do any mighty works until somebody

00:14:37.040 --> 00:14:40.150
put a demand on it.'Look at what he did

00:14:40.160 --> 00:14:42.949
with the water turning into wine.

00:14:42.959 --> 00:14:46.550
Mary put a demand on that gift

00:14:46.560 --> 00:14:50.110
inside of him. But it wasn't time

00:14:50.120 --> 00:14:52.030
yet.

00:14:52.040 --> 00:14:56.509
30

00:14:56.519 --> 00:14:59.910
years, nothing, and then somebody put a

00:14:59.920 --> 00:15:01.910
demand on it and caused that gift to

00:15:01.920 --> 00:15:04.069
flourish. And that's why I feel like a

00:15:04.079 --> 00:15:05.590
lot of times, maybe that's where we're

00:15:05.600 --> 00:15:08.710
at. Maybe it wasn't season yet. But the

00:15:08.720 --> 00:15:11.430
Lord said it's time to put a demand

00:15:11.440 --> 00:15:14.310
on what is rightfully ours. When I was

00:15:14.320 --> 00:15:16.069
driving around today, he said it's time

00:15:16.079 --> 00:15:18.870
to put a demand on it. It's time for you

00:15:18.880 --> 00:15:20.590
to

00:15:20.600 --> 00:15:22.629
expect, because I was

00:15:22.639 --> 00:15:23.750
driving under a bridge. I can't even

00:15:23.760 --> 00:15:25.269
tell you where I was. I was on

00:15:25.279 --> 00:15:28.150
Memorial Drive in Tulsa, Oklahoma. And I

00:15:28.160 --> 00:15:30.389
was going under the bridge

00:15:30.389 --> 00:15:30.399
because

00:15:30.399 --> 00:15:31.670
I was looking at the Range

00:15:31.680 --> 00:15:33.110
Rovers, I was looking at the Cadillac

00:15:33.120 --> 00:15:35.430
dealership, I was believing big.

00:15:35.440 --> 00:15:36.949
Looking at those cars and going,

00:15:36.959 --> 00:15:39.910
'Look at those cars. That's the wealth

00:15:39.920 --> 00:15:41.590
of the sinner laid up for the righteous.

00:15:41.600 --> 00:15:43.990
Look at those brand new Escalades,

00:15:44.000 --> 00:15:45.430
look at those brand new Range

00:15:45.430 --> 00:15:45.440
Rovers,

00:15:45.440 --> 00:15:47.110
look at those brand new cars. Look at

00:15:47.120 --> 00:15:50.790
what the world has.'And yes, they have

00:15:50.800 --> 00:15:52.870
it, but greater is he that is in me.

00:15:52.880 --> 00:15:54.870
Yes. He said he would provide, the

00:15:54.880 --> 00:15:56.230
wealth of the sinners is laid up for the

00:15:56.240 --> 00:15:58.470
righteous. I believe it. It's a wealth

00:15:58.480 --> 00:16:00.470
transfer time. Some people don't want to

00:16:00.480 --> 00:16:01.990
agree with me on that. That's fine, stay

00:16:02.000 --> 00:16:04.790
where you are, but don't criticize me

00:16:04.800 --> 00:16:08.470
for believing big.

00:16:08.480 --> 00:16:10.230
I was driving underneath the

00:16:10.240 --> 00:16:12.949
bridge there, and the Lord started

00:16:12.959 --> 00:16:17.189
talking to me about the angels, and he

00:16:17.199 --> 00:16:19.189
said, 'Brandon, remember I told you as

00:16:19.199 --> 00:16:21.189
you're passing under this bridge to

00:16:21.199 --> 00:16:23.749
believe for angelic visitation in

00:16:23.759 --> 00:16:26.310
these services? Believe for the angels

00:16:26.320 --> 00:16:30.110
to work with you to bring the body

00:16:30.110 --> 00:16:30.120
parts.'I

00:16:30.120 --> 00:16:32.710
told you when we got in

00:16:32.720 --> 00:16:36.870
prayer, if an octopus can

00:16:36.880 --> 00:16:39.749
get a new limb and grow back new limbs,

00:16:39.759 --> 00:16:42.230
if a crab can do it and they're

00:16:42.230 --> 00:16:42.240
sea-dwelling

00:16:42.240 --> 00:16:45.189
animals, how much more are you

00:16:45.199 --> 00:16:47.910
able to believe for a new arm or a new

00:16:47.920 --> 00:16:50.150
leg or new eyes? If they can grow back

00:16:50.160 --> 00:16:53.829
stuff, why can't we? We're created in

00:16:53.839 --> 00:16:56.790
his image. We're created to be the head

00:16:56.800 --> 00:16:58.790
over all these things. He said to take

00:16:58.800 --> 00:17:00.230
dominion and authority over these

00:17:00.240 --> 00:17:02.470
animals. How much more do we have the

00:17:02.480 --> 00:17:04.270
ability to grow back

00:17:04.280 --> 00:17:06.230
something? 'Well, I don't believe that.

00:17:06.240 --> 00:17:07.669
We've never seen it.'It's time to

00:17:07.679 --> 00:17:08.909
believe for the

00:17:08.919 --> 00:17:11.630
impossible. It's time to believe. God

00:17:11.640 --> 00:17:14.750
forbid. Are we in the last days or

00:17:14.760 --> 00:17:17.350
not? Are we going to see signs will

00:17:17.360 --> 00:17:20.029
follow them that

00:17:20.039 --> 00:17:22.949
believe? I'm so done with being a

00:17:22.959 --> 00:17:24.470
Christian that's just barely, you know,

00:17:24.480 --> 00:17:26.870
'Well, we see it, well, we may

00:17:26.870 --> 00:17:26.880
not.'Every

00:17:26.880 --> 00:17:29.830
once in a while, it's whatever, man. I'm

00:17:29.840 --> 00:17:31.990
believing for it every day.

00:17:31.990 --> 00:17:32.000
Let's

00:17:32.000 --> 00:17:34.310
believe for God to do something every

00:17:34.320 --> 00:17:37.510
day. Believe God for finances,

00:17:37.520 --> 00:17:39.669
like, we need to look nice for

00:17:39.679 --> 00:17:41.549
him. We represent the

00:17:41.559 --> 00:17:43.990
King. He's corrected me about my

00:17:44.000 --> 00:17:45.750
clothes. He's corrected me about a lot

00:17:45.760 --> 00:17:47.510
of things, saying, "Brandon, you

00:17:47.520 --> 00:17:49.390
represent me. You need to look nice for

00:17:49.400 --> 00:17:51.990
me. When you go into public, you

00:17:52.000 --> 00:17:53.350
need to look nice. Don't wear your

00:17:53.360 --> 00:17:55.590
scrubby stuff out and always have holes.

00:17:55.600 --> 00:17:59.510
Look nice for me. Look

00:17:59.510 --> 00:17:59.520
nice."Why?

00:17:59.520 --> 00:18:02.549
Because John G. Lake used to

00:18:02.559 --> 00:18:04.230
look in the mirror. He put on a white

00:18:04.240 --> 00:18:06.070
suit, a white tie, and all these

00:18:06.080 --> 00:18:08.549
white clothes. And he looked

00:18:08.549 --> 00:18:08.559
and

00:18:08.559 --> 00:18:10.150
said, "God dwells on the inside

00:18:10.160 --> 00:18:12.230
of this man, and I

00:18:12.240 --> 00:18:13.549
represent

00:18:13.559 --> 00:18:16.150
him. I represent the King of Kings and

00:18:16.160 --> 00:18:18.789
the Lord of Lords. And he dwells on the

00:18:18.799 --> 00:18:21.990
inside of this

00:18:21.990 --> 00:18:22.000
man."So

00:18:22.000 --> 00:18:23.830
I started thinking about what John G.

00:18:23.840 --> 00:18:26.750
Lake did, and he had an appearance of

00:18:26.760 --> 00:18:29.350
excellence. His car was clean. Things

00:18:29.350 --> 00:18:29.360
looked

00:18:29.360 --> 00:18:31.909
nice. When you represent the King,

00:18:31.919 --> 00:18:34.470
you look nice. You clean yourself up.

00:18:34.480 --> 00:18:36.150
You may not have a dime to your name,

00:18:36.160 --> 00:18:38.390
but a bar of soap only costs so

00:18:38.400 --> 00:18:39.750
much. And you look nice with a bar of

00:18:39.760 --> 00:18:41.110
soap. You don't have to look scruffy and

00:18:41.120 --> 00:18:46.070
dirty, with oily hair. You

00:18:46.080 --> 00:18:48.470
can have an appearance of cleanliness,

00:18:48.480 --> 00:18:50.710
too, because cleanliness is godliness. My mom

00:18:50.720 --> 00:18:52.950
would always say, "Cleanliness is

00:18:52.950 --> 00:18:52.960
godliness."I

00:18:52.960 --> 00:18:54.870
say, "Well, you don't have

00:18:54.880 --> 00:18:57.750
to stink with B.O.. You can have a

00:18:57.760 --> 00:19:00.070
bar of soap, scrub your armpits down,

00:19:00.070 --> 00:19:00.080
and

00:19:00.080 --> 00:19:02.470
make yourself smell nice."I mean,

00:19:02.480 --> 00:19:04.870
there's a point of appearance,

00:19:04.870 --> 00:19:04.880
an

00:19:04.880 --> 00:19:07.590
appearance of excellence, showing

00:19:07.600 --> 00:19:10.830
up and believing God for

00:19:10.840 --> 00:19:13.190
more. Believing God for more. Well,

00:19:13.200 --> 00:19:15.430
this guy said, "I believe in God.

00:19:15.440 --> 00:19:17.430
Do you think the Lord wants me to have a

00:19:17.440 --> 00:19:19.430
new car, brother?"That's what I'm

00:19:19.440 --> 00:19:20.470
talking about, driving around looking at

00:19:20.480 --> 00:19:22.230
that. That's when I heard Brother

00:19:22.230 --> 00:19:22.240
Hagin

00:19:22.240 --> 00:19:24.390
teaching that today. I said, "Let's go

00:19:24.400 --> 00:19:25.630
look at the

00:19:25.640 --> 00:19:28.630
Cadillacs. Let's go look at the

00:19:28.640 --> 00:19:31.870
Range Rovers. Let's go look for

00:19:31.870 --> 00:19:31.880
more."Because

00:19:31.880 --> 00:19:34.950
he said, "Is it

00:19:34.960 --> 00:19:37.270
wrong to have a brand new car? Is it

00:19:37.280 --> 00:19:39.350
wrong to not be buying used all the

00:19:39.350 --> 00:19:39.360
time?"And

00:19:39.360 --> 00:19:41.510
he said, "You're representing

00:19:41.520 --> 00:19:42.350
the

00:19:42.360 --> 00:19:45.270
King. You're representing the King. And

00:19:45.280 --> 00:19:47.270
if you, being evil, give good gifts to

00:19:47.280 --> 00:19:49.350
your kids, how much more does your

00:19:49.360 --> 00:19:51.590
Heavenly Father give good gifts to those

00:19:51.600 --> 00:19:54.590
that love him and are hearing

00:19:54.600 --> 00:19:57.990
him? How much more?"So I started

00:19:58.000 --> 00:19:59.950
thinking, well, why not believe for

00:19:59.960 --> 00:20:03.669
bigger? Why not believe God for more?

00:20:03.679 --> 00:20:05.990
Why not believe God for a newer house?

00:20:06.000 --> 00:20:08.789
Why not believe God for this stuff? I

00:20:08.799 --> 00:20:10.310
believed for this house that I'm living

00:20:10.320 --> 00:20:11.590
in right now, and it's time. And the

00:20:11.600 --> 00:20:12.710
Lord said, "Brandon, look what I gave

00:20:12.720 --> 00:20:15.350
you this time last year. Look

00:20:15.360 --> 00:20:17.029
how I took care of you this time

00:20:17.039 --> 00:20:18.630
last year."I was sitting on my back

00:20:18.640 --> 00:20:21.590
patio. I lived in a shotgun house in

00:20:21.600 --> 00:20:23.310
Guthrie,

00:20:23.320 --> 00:20:26.310
Oklahoma. Bad mice coming in. We had

00:20:26.320 --> 00:20:28.470
rodents. We had snakes coming up through

00:20:28.480 --> 00:20:30.230
the floorboards. Our house had

00:20:30.240 --> 00:20:32.470
mold so bad we were falling through the

00:20:32.480 --> 00:20:34.990
foundation of the

00:20:35.000 --> 00:20:37.950
floor. Lived there for

00:20:37.960 --> 00:20:43.270
22 years. 22 years my kids,

00:20:43.280 --> 00:20:45.510
all of them born in there, lived

00:20:45.520 --> 00:20:47.510
there all those years, being a janitor at

00:20:47.520 --> 00:20:51.390
the church, making nothing,

00:20:51.390 --> 00:20:51.400
believing

00:20:51.400 --> 00:20:53.909
God, believing God. And the Lord said,

00:20:53.919 --> 00:20:55.270
"Stay here. Take care of your

00:20:55.270 --> 00:20:55.280
grandma."I

00:20:55.280 --> 00:20:56.870
took care of my grandmother all that

00:20:56.880 --> 00:20:59.750
time. I complained—I'm not

00:20:59.760 --> 00:21:01.190
going to lie to y'all, I did complain to

00:21:01.200 --> 00:21:03.190
the Lord. "Lord, I need something better. My

00:21:03.190 --> 00:21:03.200
family—the

00:21:03.200 --> 00:21:05.350
mold and mildew smell in here

00:21:05.350 --> 00:21:05.360
is

00:21:05.360 --> 00:21:07.590
so bad, all the things that we dealt with

00:21:07.600 --> 00:21:09.149
for so many

00:21:09.149 --> 00:21:09.159
years."But

00:21:09.159 --> 00:21:12.710
God came through and got us

00:21:12.720 --> 00:21:15.470
this house we're living in

00:21:15.480 --> 00:21:17.909
now. 23 years. And people say, "Well,

00:21:17.909 --> 00:21:17.919
Brandon,

00:21:17.919 --> 00:21:19.510
your house is nice now."But you

00:21:19.520 --> 00:21:21.750
don't know what I came from. You don't

00:21:21.760 --> 00:21:24.230
know what God did. I never get mad at

00:21:24.240 --> 00:21:25.750
somebody's blessing whenever you see

00:21:25.760 --> 00:21:26.870
what they have and where they are,

00:21:26.880 --> 00:21:28.390
because you don't know what seeds they

00:21:28.400 --> 00:21:30.350
sowed to get what they've

00:21:30.360 --> 00:21:33.190
got. I rejoice whenever I see

00:21:33.200 --> 00:21:35.909
